      <p><strong>Cookies</strong></p>
      <p>A cookie is a text file containing information that can be remembered by a web browser between pages. When an individual uses a web browser (e.g. Firefox, Chrome, Internet Explorer etc) to access the internet, that browser can create cookies which are stored on the user’s computer. Cookies are not programs and therefore cannot contain viruses or other malicious software. They are purely a string of text and numbers.</p>
      <p><strong>Our Use Of Cookies</strong></p>
